Plot: A CSIS agent must call to the help of a mentally-unstable musical "genius" to uncover the mysterious disappearances at a local college. Meanwhile a group of LARPers start their own investigation.
Title: Sassquatch: Return of the Queen
Writer: Tyler Boyco, Ian McCartney (storyliner), Jeegar Thakker (story)
Actors: Tyler Boyco, Tyler Mclellan, Lydia Dawson, Shawn Scott
